<%# app/views/booking_mailer/refund_confirmation.text.erb %>
Refund Confirmed — The Anchorpoint Retreat
=============================================

Dear <%= @booking.guest_name %>,

Your booking at The Anchorpoint Retreat has been refunded successfully.

Confirmation Number: <%= @booking.confirmation_number %>

REFUND DETAILS
--------------
Refund Amount:      <%= @refund_amount %>
Original Check-in:  <%= @booking.check_in.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>
Original Check-out: <%= @booking.check_out.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>

The refund has been processed and will be returned to your original payment
method. Depending on your bank or card issuer, it may take 5-10 business days
to appear on your statement.

We're sorry to see you go. If you'd like to rebook in the future, we'd be happy
to host you.

Warm regards,
The Anchorpoint Retreat Team

---
This email was sent to <%= @booking.guest_email %>.
